1
00:00:06,600 --> 00:00:11,537
=The Moment I Met You=

2
00:00:11,537 --> 00:00:14,987
=Episode 21=

3
00:00:15,062 --> 00:00:20,162
(Zhengyang Gate)

4
00:00:20,879 --> 00:00:23,280
Squire Mei, this setup looks professional.

5
00:00:24,079 --> 00:00:25,079
Impressive.

6
00:00:26,120 --> 00:00:28,079
I'm just doing some last-minute cramming.

7
00:00:28,125 --> 00:00:29,887
(Zhengyang Gate)

8
00:00:30,440 --> 00:00:31,039
Buyu,

9
00:00:31,719 --> 00:00:34,159
to be honest,
my lightness skill isn't great either.

10
00:00:34,159 --> 00:00:35,280
But for Chang's sake,

11
00:00:35,679 --> 00:00:37,439
we'll just have to practice together.

12
00:00:37,439 --> 00:00:38,600
Alright, let's begin.

13
00:00:39,240 --> 00:00:40,240
I'm ready.

14
00:00:40,359 --> 00:00:40,960
Good.

15
00:00:44,079 --> 00:00:44,799
Who's that?

16
00:00:45,719 --> 00:00:46,359
Who goes there?

17
00:00:46,950 --> 00:00:47,800
(Zhengyang Gate)

18
00:00:47,960 --> 00:00:48,560
Who is it?

19
00:00:48,600 --> 00:00:49,412
(Zhengyang Gate)

20
00:00:53,479 --> 00:00:54,799
That was amazing, Squire!

21
00:00:55,079 --> 00:00:57,000
It must take decades
to master a move like that.

22
00:00:57,600 --> 00:00:59,039
Stop with the flattery.

23
00:00:59,399 --> 00:01:01,960
This move is
called "Feinting to the East".

24
00:01:02,399 --> 00:01:02,920
Understand?

25
00:01:03,079 --> 00:01:03,719
I understand.

26
00:01:05,280 --> 00:01:06,519
Now, let's see you try it.

27
00:01:09,837 --> 00:01:10,957
(What are they doing?)

28
00:01:11,525 --> 00:01:13,625
(Zhengyang Gate, Prosperity for Family)

29
00:01:16,925 --> 00:01:17,640
Up!

30
00:01:17,640 --> 00:01:18,475
(Zhengyang Gate, Prosperity for Family)

31
00:01:28,280 --> 00:01:28,840
Buyu!

32
00:01:29,037 --> 00:01:29,750
(Zhengyang Gate, Prosperity for Family)

33
00:01:41,640 --> 00:01:42,560
Young Master Shen!

34
00:01:46,359 --> 00:01:47,239
I'm sorry!

35
00:01:47,680 --> 00:01:48,319
Who are you?

36
00:01:48,319 --> 00:01:49,439
I didn't mean it.

37
00:01:50,840 --> 00:01:51,799
Excuse me for a moment.

38
00:01:53,439 --> 00:01:54,000
Right.

39
00:02:05,000 --> 00:02:05,680
Come in.

40
00:02:11,759 --> 00:02:12,560
I didn't realize

41
00:02:12,800 --> 00:02:14,680
your skin was so fair.

42
00:02:15,639 --> 00:02:16,680
How much did you see?

43
00:02:17,879 --> 00:02:19,240
I didn't see anything at all.

44
00:02:20,319 --> 00:02:21,360
You're a grown man,

45
00:02:21,360 --> 00:02:22,680
why are you being so shy?

46
00:02:26,719 --> 00:02:27,780
Do you have business here?

47
00:02:28,599 --> 00:02:30,639
Of course I have business.

48
00:02:31,039 --> 00:02:32,960
I just made some honey cakes

49
00:02:33,199 --> 00:02:34,800
and brought them for you to try.

50
00:02:35,120 --> 00:02:35,759
Thanks.

51
00:02:36,000 --> 00:02:38,520
See? I am good at cooking

52
00:02:38,520 --> 00:02:39,520
and socializing.

53
00:02:39,599 --> 00:02:40,919
I'll eat the cakes.

54
00:02:42,599 --> 00:02:43,199
Now leave.

55
00:02:44,599 --> 00:02:45,199
Sure.

56
00:02:55,199 --> 00:02:56,439
Let's try some.

57
00:02:59,159 --> 00:03:00,000
What's over there?

58
00:03:00,625 --> 00:03:02,412
(Zhengyang Gate)

59
00:03:02,560 --> 00:03:03,400
Hold this. One more.

60
00:03:03,400 --> 00:03:04,080
Sure. Thank you.

61
00:03:04,080 --> 00:03:04,639
Alright.

62
00:03:04,639 --> 00:03:05,439
(Zhengyang Gate)

63
00:03:05,439 --> 00:03:06,280
Come again.

64
00:03:11,360 --> 00:03:12,159
Grab the money!

65
00:03:14,560 --> 00:03:15,199
Money!

66
00:03:16,180 --> 00:03:16,719
This is mine!

67
00:03:16,759 --> 00:03:17,199
Mine!

68
00:03:18,360 --> 00:03:18,840
It's mine!

69
00:03:18,879 --> 00:03:19,319
More here!

70
00:03:19,719 --> 00:03:20,159
Mine!

71
00:03:20,159 --> 00:03:21,162
(Zhengyang Gate)

72
00:03:21,319 --> 00:03:22,159
Don't step on it!

73
00:03:24,512 --> 00:03:26,375
(Zhengyang Gate)

74
00:03:28,919 --> 00:03:31,599
(Zhengyang Gate)
Don't grab it! I saw it first!

75
00:03:31,800 --> 00:03:32,800
This is mine.

76
00:03:33,439 --> 00:03:33,879
Mine!

77
00:03:35,599 --> 00:03:36,199
Time to dash.

78
00:03:47,360 --> 00:03:48,360
What do you want now?

79
00:03:48,960 --> 00:03:51,120
(Marriage Contract)
The contract you're holding.

80
00:03:53,560 --> 00:03:54,759
Why would I give it to you?

81
00:03:55,479 --> 00:03:56,479
I can always

82
00:03:57,240 --> 00:03:58,360
just rob you.

83
00:03:59,120 --> 00:04:00,120
In that case,

84
00:04:01,360 --> 00:04:02,280
go ahead and try.

85
00:04:20,800 --> 00:04:22,480
You don't even know your opponent.

86
00:04:22,500 --> 00:04:24,319
How did you expect
to beat the Bandit Prince?

87
00:04:26,079 --> 00:04:26,959
Give it to me.

88
00:04:33,399 --> 00:04:34,079
Thanks.

89
00:04:42,879 --> 00:04:43,600
I won.

90
00:04:46,680 --> 00:04:47,519
You coward.

91
00:04:47,920 --> 00:04:48,800
You tricked me

92
00:04:48,800 --> 00:04:50,000
into giving up the contract.

93
00:04:50,000 --> 00:04:50,839
It wasn't a fair win!

94
00:04:52,199 --> 00:04:53,920
All's fair in love and war.

95
00:04:54,759 --> 00:04:56,399
The contract is mine now.

96
00:04:56,399 --> 00:04:57,360
Ms. Chu,

97
00:04:57,639 --> 00:04:58,519
what do you say?

98
00:05:00,750 --> 00:05:01,720
I don't mind either way.

99
00:05:02,959 --> 00:05:03,560
You...

100
00:05:07,240 --> 00:05:07,879
It seems

101
00:05:07,879 --> 00:05:09,600
you haven't settled this yet.

102
00:05:10,519 --> 00:05:11,439
Please, continue.

103
00:05:12,360 --> 00:05:13,600
What's left to settle?

104
00:05:13,800 --> 00:05:15,079
I have the contract.

105
00:05:15,360 --> 00:05:16,600
The winner

106
00:05:17,000 --> 00:05:17,959
is obvious.

107
00:05:17,959 --> 00:05:18,519
You...

108
00:05:25,000 --> 00:05:26,519
I never thought the great Bandit Prince

109
00:05:26,600 --> 00:05:28,519
would resort to such low-life tactics.

110
00:05:29,187 --> 00:05:29,708
What?

111
00:05:30,879 --> 00:05:32,800
I've no idea what you're talking about.

112
00:05:33,770 --> 00:05:35,680
Did you really think
I'd fall for your hypnosis?

113
00:05:36,399 --> 00:05:37,279
Take a look.

114
00:05:37,920 --> 00:05:38,720
What's this?

115
00:05:39,720 --> 00:05:41,199
I should tell you something else.

116
00:05:41,639 --> 00:05:42,680
Shen Liefeng

117
00:05:42,879 --> 00:05:43,920
isn't just fast.

118
00:05:43,920 --> 00:05:45,959
He's also a master of hypnosis.

119
00:05:46,879 --> 00:05:47,800
Hypnosis?

120
00:05:48,879 --> 00:05:51,519
In the West, they call it hypnotism.

121
00:05:51,759 --> 00:05:54,160
It's said he can control the mind.

122
00:05:54,319 --> 00:05:57,079
Remember, whatever you do,
don't look into his eyes.

123
00:06:03,720 --> 00:06:04,319
You...

124
00:06:04,639 --> 00:06:06,759
I knew you'd try to use illusions.

125
00:06:07,000 --> 00:06:08,720
So I plugged my ears

126
00:06:08,839 --> 00:06:10,079
and avoided your gaze.

127
00:06:11,000 --> 00:06:12,680
I just wanted to see
who you really were.

128
00:06:13,360 --> 00:06:14,412
But you got so cocky

129
00:06:14,412 --> 00:06:16,011
that you'd expose your own identity.

130
00:06:20,120 --> 00:06:21,360
Have you got it figured out now?

131
00:06:30,120 --> 00:06:32,319
Buyu, he's the Xichuan Bandit Prince.

132
00:06:33,759 --> 00:06:34,399
Buyu,

133
00:06:34,920 --> 00:06:36,040
now you believe me, right?

134
00:06:36,040 --> 00:06:37,839
I know he's the Bandit Prince.

135
00:06:38,240 --> 00:06:39,680
I was talking about Chu Yunchang!

136
00:06:42,040 --> 00:06:43,160
Nothing to do with her.

137
00:06:43,362 --> 00:06:44,802
How can you be so dense?

138
00:06:46,600 --> 00:06:49,199
If her fiancé is
the Xichuan Bandit Prince,

139
00:06:49,519 --> 00:06:50,639
then that begs the question.

140
00:06:51,160 --> 00:06:52,480
Who exactly is Chu Yunchang?

141
00:06:52,600 --> 00:06:55,199
How does she have a marriage contract
with Shuzhong's thief sect?

142
00:06:56,360 --> 00:06:59,040
Chu Yunchang, what do you
have to say for yourself?

143
00:07:01,310 --> 00:07:03,959
You're saying he's the Bandit Prince,
and since I'm engaged to him,

144
00:07:03,959 --> 00:07:05,160
I must be a criminal too.

145
00:07:05,480 --> 00:07:06,120
Is that right?

146
00:07:06,560 --> 00:07:07,319
Exactly.

147
00:07:08,360 --> 00:07:09,480
Well, look at it another way.

148
00:07:10,360 --> 00:07:11,879
If I prove he's not the Bandit Prince,

149
00:07:12,120 --> 00:07:13,399
wouldn't that prove

150
00:07:13,399 --> 00:07:14,199
that I'm innocent?

151
00:07:14,800 --> 00:07:16,839
If he's not the Bandit Prince,
then who is he?

152
00:07:18,120 --> 00:07:18,759
Fine.

153
00:07:19,439 --> 00:07:21,920
If you can prove he's not
the Bandit Prince of Xichuan,

154
00:07:21,920 --> 00:07:23,600
then I'll have reason to believe

155
00:07:24,279 --> 00:07:25,720
you aren't that thieving rat.

156
00:07:26,759 --> 00:07:27,360
Zhizhi,

157
00:07:27,360 --> 00:07:28,000
do it!

158
00:07:50,519 --> 00:07:51,279
Who are you?

159
00:07:53,160 --> 00:07:53,720
Yunchang,

160
00:07:54,360 --> 00:07:56,759
why is a man wearing a woman's bodice?

161
00:08:01,560 --> 00:08:02,600
See for yourselves.

162
00:08:03,160 --> 00:08:04,160
Who is this really?

163
00:08:06,360 --> 00:08:08,360
How can the Xichuan Bandit Prince
be a woman?

164
00:08:09,240 --> 00:08:09,879
Rong,

165
00:08:10,839 --> 00:08:11,959
you're with the Intel Corps.

166
00:08:12,600 --> 00:08:13,519
Tell me.

167
00:08:14,000 --> 00:08:15,279
According to the records,

168
00:08:15,759 --> 00:08:18,000
is the Bandit Prince a man or a woman?

169
00:08:18,360 --> 00:08:18,920
Well...

170
00:08:19,600 --> 00:08:21,040
He's a man.

171
00:08:21,839 --> 00:08:22,920
Now, look at her.

172
00:08:23,839 --> 00:08:25,800
Is that a man or a woman to you?

173
00:08:28,800 --> 00:08:29,519
My head hurts...

174
00:08:29,720 --> 00:08:30,319
Yunchang,

175
00:08:30,439 --> 00:08:31,800
what's going on here?

176
00:08:32,159 --> 00:08:33,000
Explain yourself.

177
00:08:33,600 --> 00:08:34,519
Who are you, really?

178
00:08:36,120 --> 00:08:36,720
I...

179
00:08:37,320 --> 00:08:39,600
Keep your mouth shut
if you want to stay alive.

180
00:08:41,519 --> 00:08:43,480
I'm definitely not the Bandit Prince.

181
00:08:45,279 --> 00:08:47,120
If you aren't the Bandit Prince,

182
00:08:47,120 --> 00:08:49,080
why did you use his name to propose?

183
00:08:49,960 --> 00:08:51,080
I...

184
00:08:52,162 --> 00:08:52,802
Chang,

185
00:08:53,720 --> 00:08:54,679
what's going on?

186
00:08:57,200 --> 00:08:58,480
Allow me to explain.

187
00:09:03,320 --> 00:09:04,039
Buyu,

188
00:09:04,559 --> 00:09:06,919
this was actually the final test

189
00:09:07,159 --> 00:09:08,600
the Chu family had for you.

190
00:09:10,200 --> 00:09:10,919
A test?

191
00:09:12,080 --> 00:09:12,960
What test?

192
00:09:14,399 --> 00:09:16,240
You wanted to marry Yunchang, right?

193
00:09:16,840 --> 00:09:20,399
But her aunt still had some reservations.

194
00:09:21,000 --> 00:09:22,720
So we found this girl

195
00:09:24,120 --> 00:09:26,159
to dress as a man and fake a proposal.

196
00:09:26,519 --> 00:09:27,480
The duel was just a ruse

197
00:09:28,080 --> 00:09:30,000
to see if your heart was true.

198
00:09:30,480 --> 00:09:32,200
My devotion to Chang
is beyond any doubt.

199
00:09:32,879 --> 00:09:34,120
Why won't you believe me?

200
00:09:34,720 --> 00:09:37,159
We had our doubts before, it's true.

201
00:09:37,519 --> 00:09:39,600
But now, we're completely convinced.

202
00:09:43,480 --> 00:09:44,720
That was a smooth recovery.

203
00:09:45,720 --> 00:09:47,320
Do you think we're children?

204
00:09:47,679 --> 00:09:49,120
Hiring someone to test Buyu?

205
00:09:50,559 --> 00:09:51,320
Deputy Luo,

206
00:09:51,639 --> 00:09:54,120
then what do you think our motive was?

207
00:09:54,759 --> 00:09:55,919
I think you...

208
00:10:00,559 --> 00:10:01,200
Chang,

209
00:10:02,480 --> 00:10:04,399
did you know about this from the start?

210
00:10:08,039 --> 00:10:08,679
Buyu,

211
00:10:09,480 --> 00:10:11,039
of course she didn't know anything.

212
00:10:11,320 --> 00:10:13,000
We only told her after the fact.

213
00:10:13,720 --> 00:10:15,039
Please, don't be angry.

214
00:10:15,120 --> 00:10:17,200
She's the only daughter
of the Chu family.

215
00:10:17,480 --> 00:10:19,480
She's the light of our lives.

216
00:10:19,600 --> 00:10:21,120
Naturally, we were extremely anxious

217
00:10:21,120 --> 00:10:22,279
about her marriage.

218
00:10:22,639 --> 00:10:23,440
But as of now,

219
00:10:23,440 --> 00:10:26,240
the Chu family has
officially accepted you

220
00:10:26,500 --> 00:10:27,519
as our future son-in-law.

221
00:10:32,200 --> 00:10:34,480
I don't believe
a single word you're saying.

222
00:10:34,679 --> 00:10:36,120
Hiring someone to test him?

223
00:10:36,210 --> 00:10:38,120
Where did the name
Shen Liefeng come from then?

224
00:10:39,320 --> 00:10:40,559
I just made it up on the spot.

225
00:10:41,530 --> 00:10:43,879
What a coincidence to share
a name with the Bandit Prince.

226
00:10:43,879 --> 00:10:44,799
Why not?

227
00:10:45,240 --> 00:10:46,159
It's not like we knew

228
00:10:46,159 --> 00:10:48,320
what the Bandit Prince was called.

229
00:10:48,320 --> 00:10:48,919
Fine.

230
00:10:49,039 --> 00:10:50,639
You, woman of mystery,

231
00:10:50,799 --> 00:10:52,159
you're coming back for questioning.

232
00:10:53,159 --> 00:10:54,039
I'm not going! No way!

233
00:10:54,559 --> 00:10:55,240
Hold on.

234
00:10:56,470 --> 00:10:57,980
On what grounds are you arresting her?

235
00:10:58,519 --> 00:10:59,399
Exactly, Wushuang.

236
00:10:59,519 --> 00:11:01,279
You can't just arrest someone

237
00:11:01,279 --> 00:11:02,039
for cross-dressing.

238
00:11:02,039 --> 00:11:02,799
Right!

239
00:11:02,799 --> 00:11:04,279
Say something!

240
00:11:08,799 --> 00:11:09,480
I...

241
00:11:10,559 --> 00:11:11,770
This is absolutely ridiculous!

242
00:11:30,559 --> 00:11:31,159
Zhizhi,

243
00:11:33,159 --> 00:11:35,200
take this young lady back.

244
00:11:35,559 --> 00:11:36,320
And settle the bill.

245
00:11:39,279 --> 00:11:39,919
The bill?

246
00:11:40,759 --> 00:11:41,799
What bill?

247
00:11:43,919 --> 00:11:46,200
You don't expect her
to work for free, do you?

248
00:11:48,639 --> 00:11:50,240
Right, of course. Miss,

249
00:11:50,240 --> 00:11:51,720
come with me, I'll pay you.

250
00:11:52,039 --> 00:11:52,639
Sure.

251
00:11:58,720 --> 00:11:59,559
Carry on.

252
00:12:06,559 --> 00:12:08,290
Why did you join
the others in deceiving me?

253
00:12:10,399 --> 00:12:11,080
I...

254
00:12:11,080 --> 00:12:12,159
Others may not know me,

255
00:12:12,639 --> 00:12:13,679
but you do.

256
00:12:15,720 --> 00:12:17,200
The way the Chu family handles things

257
00:12:17,840 --> 00:12:19,039
is truly excessive.

258
00:12:20,519 --> 00:12:22,159
Buyu, please let me explain.

259
00:12:22,399 --> 00:12:23,519
Just listen to me!

260
00:12:28,840 --> 00:12:29,559
Get down.

261
00:12:29,840 --> 00:12:30,559
Not a chance.

262
00:12:31,240 --> 00:12:32,759
You can at least stop choking me.

263
00:12:36,399 --> 00:12:37,240
From the look of it,

264
00:12:37,240 --> 00:12:38,919
maybe you don't want me
to let go anyway.

265
00:12:39,960 --> 00:12:41,399
I despise deception.

266
00:12:41,780 --> 00:12:43,679
It seems you don't find me
worthy of your trust.

267
00:12:45,840 --> 00:12:47,399
That is not true. I know I was wrong.

268
00:12:47,399 --> 00:12:48,840
I will never do it again.

269
00:12:49,639 --> 00:12:51,279
Please, stop being angry with me.

270
00:12:51,279 --> 00:12:51,919
No.

271
00:12:52,800 --> 00:12:53,720
I need some time alone.

272
00:12:53,799 --> 00:12:54,720
Do not follow me.

273
00:13:00,279 --> 00:13:01,240
That was uptight.

274
00:13:03,159 --> 00:13:03,840
Miss,

275
00:13:04,080 --> 00:13:05,559
if you have doubts about her identity,

276
00:13:05,799 --> 00:13:07,480
I can seize her
for questioning in secret.

277
00:13:07,799 --> 00:13:09,000
Not without evidence.

278
00:13:15,080 --> 00:13:17,440
Send a pigeon to the brothers
at the Xichuan Bureau

279
00:13:18,080 --> 00:13:19,950
that I want all the case files
on Shen Liefeng,

280
00:13:20,039 --> 00:13:20,919
the Bandit Prince.

281
00:13:20,919 --> 00:13:22,130
The more detailed, the better.

282
00:13:22,320 --> 00:13:22,960
Yes.

283
00:13:29,919 --> 00:13:31,600
Who exactly are you?

284
00:13:32,039 --> 00:13:33,600
I truly am the Xichuan Bandit Prince.

285
00:13:33,799 --> 00:13:34,519
Nonsense!

286
00:13:34,800 --> 00:13:36,120
The Bandit Prince can't be a girl.

287
00:13:37,799 --> 00:13:39,080
If you refuse to tell the truth,

288
00:13:39,679 --> 00:13:41,200
we might lose our patience.

289
00:13:41,679 --> 00:13:42,720
You saved my life.

290
00:13:43,360 --> 00:13:44,840
How could I not tell you the truth?

291
00:13:45,600 --> 00:13:47,919
(Shen Yidie, Daughter of the Shen Family from Xichuan)
My real name is Shen Yidie.

292
00:13:48,960 --> 00:13:50,600
Shen Liefeng is my brother.

293
00:13:51,762 --> 00:13:54,402
Then he should be the actual
Xichuan Bandit Prince.

294
00:13:56,600 --> 00:13:59,720
My brother suffered
a stroke when he was seven.

295
00:14:00,310 --> 00:14:01,639
It left him permanently disabled.

296
00:14:02,660 --> 00:14:04,559
My father always
favored sons over daughters.

297
00:14:04,879 --> 00:14:05,639
He placed all of

298
00:14:05,639 --> 00:14:07,440
his hopes and expectations
on my brother.

299
00:14:08,279 --> 00:14:10,559
Unfortunately, because of his condition,

300
00:14:11,000 --> 00:14:12,880
my brother couldn't
take over the family legacy.

301
00:14:13,399 --> 00:14:14,759
But my father refused to give up.

302
00:14:14,759 --> 00:14:16,960
He feared the title of Bandit Prince
would be stolen.

303
00:14:17,399 --> 00:14:19,080
So he forced me
to practice martial arts.

304
00:14:19,879 --> 00:14:21,960
He ordered me to dress as a man

305
00:14:22,279 --> 00:14:23,840
and learn lightness skills and thievery.

306
00:14:24,159 --> 00:14:26,279
I lost every trace of being a girl.

307
00:14:26,919 --> 00:14:28,240
My father announced to the world

308
00:14:29,639 --> 00:14:30,840
that I was my brother.

309
00:14:32,200 --> 00:14:33,100
Meanwhile, my brother

310
00:14:33,360 --> 00:14:35,720
was kept hidden away at home forever.

311
00:14:36,639 --> 00:14:37,759
How could he do that?

312
00:14:38,759 --> 00:14:39,960
When I grew up,

313
00:14:40,919 --> 00:14:43,559
my father officially passed
the title of Bandit Prince to me.

314
00:14:44,240 --> 00:14:47,000
But I am a woman, after all.

315
00:14:47,240 --> 00:14:48,600
I would eventually have to marry.

316
00:14:48,919 --> 00:14:49,720
If that happened,

317
00:14:49,720 --> 00:14:51,559
the title of Bandit Prince
would be lost.

318
00:14:51,840 --> 00:14:54,279
Then, my father remembered the old joke

319
00:14:54,279 --> 00:14:56,919
about the betrothal contract
with your grandfather.

320
00:14:57,799 --> 00:14:58,759
My father realized

321
00:14:59,000 --> 00:15:01,440
that an alliance with the Chu family
and the Sacred Hand Sect

322
00:15:01,799 --> 00:15:03,240
would solidify our family's standing

323
00:15:03,240 --> 00:15:05,399
among Xichuan's thieves.

324
00:15:06,759 --> 00:15:09,159
So I was forced to follow his orders

325
00:15:10,000 --> 00:15:11,399
and come here in my brother's place

326
00:15:11,840 --> 00:15:13,360
to marry Ms. Chu.

327
00:15:15,240 --> 00:15:15,960
But

328
00:15:16,879 --> 00:15:18,240
your maid happened

329
00:15:18,559 --> 00:15:20,039
to see through my disguise.

330
00:15:20,679 --> 00:15:22,240
So you were basically planning

331
00:15:22,240 --> 00:15:23,200
to trick Chang into

332
00:15:23,200 --> 00:15:24,799
marrying your disabled brother

333
00:15:24,799 --> 00:15:25,879
just to produce an heir?

334
00:15:27,799 --> 00:15:30,279
Your father is too selfish and cruel.

335
00:15:45,360 --> 00:15:47,120
Did you have a fight with Yunchang?

336
00:15:49,559 --> 00:15:50,120
Sister,

337
00:15:50,840 --> 00:15:52,480
how could her family play me like that?

338
00:15:52,480 --> 00:15:53,759
Didn't you always say

339
00:15:53,759 --> 00:15:55,279
your devotion to Chu Yunchang

340
00:15:55,279 --> 00:15:56,600
was beyond any doubt?

341
00:15:56,600 --> 00:15:58,279
And now you are this angry over this?

342
00:15:58,399 --> 00:15:58,960
I...

343
00:16:00,960 --> 00:16:03,759
You aren't just upset
because the family tested you.

344
00:16:03,879 --> 00:16:05,000
There is more to it.

345
00:16:06,260 --> 00:16:07,559
Don't you find this suspicious?

346
00:16:08,360 --> 00:16:09,279
To test me,

347
00:16:09,559 --> 00:16:11,519
they hired a woman to pose as a man.

348
00:16:12,720 --> 00:16:13,399
Could it be

349
00:16:13,679 --> 00:16:15,559
she knew that Wushuang would intervene?

350
00:16:18,600 --> 00:16:19,600
And of all names,

351
00:16:19,620 --> 00:16:21,679
she chose to call herself
the Xichuan Bandit Prince.

352
00:16:22,799 --> 00:16:23,639
Furthermore,

353
00:16:23,879 --> 00:16:25,799
that woman was
far too skilled in lightness

354
00:16:25,799 --> 00:16:26,679
and illusion.

355
00:16:27,879 --> 00:16:29,440
Does that really seem like a mere act?

356
00:16:30,679 --> 00:16:31,720
If you have such doubts,

357
00:16:31,960 --> 00:16:33,399
why didn't you speak up at the shop?

358
00:16:36,000 --> 00:16:37,960
You were still trying
to protect the Chu family.

359
00:16:38,559 --> 00:16:39,600
But tell me, Buyu,

360
00:16:39,840 --> 00:16:41,240
is it possible they are actually...

361
00:16:41,240 --> 00:16:41,960
Sister.

362
00:16:42,370 --> 00:16:44,690
Without concrete evidence,
we shouldn't make accusations.

363
00:16:45,240 --> 00:16:45,919
Fine.

364
00:16:46,320 --> 00:16:47,279
But I believe

365
00:16:47,440 --> 00:16:49,200
if your feelings for Yunchang are real,

366
00:16:49,200 --> 00:16:50,559
you should go find the proof.

367
00:16:50,679 --> 00:16:53,039
At least prove
that her family is innocent.

368
00:16:53,320 --> 00:16:54,679
But if you're truly concerned,

369
00:16:54,679 --> 00:16:55,480
- then...
- Sister.

370
00:16:55,519 --> 00:16:56,360
Say no more.

371
00:16:56,879 --> 00:16:58,039
I will find the evidence.

372
00:16:58,060 --> 00:16:59,399
I'll prove Yunchang is innocent.

373
00:17:06,119 --> 00:17:06,759
Sect Leader,

374
00:17:07,640 --> 00:17:09,240
I apologize for the trouble I caused.

375
00:17:09,880 --> 00:17:11,559
If you ever need
assistance in the future,

376
00:17:11,759 --> 00:17:14,359
the Xichuan outlaws
will be at your service.

377
00:17:14,960 --> 00:17:15,440
You really

378
00:17:15,440 --> 00:17:17,200
should have a serious talk
with your father.

379
00:17:17,580 --> 00:17:19,400
We are people
of the martial world, after all.

380
00:17:19,680 --> 00:17:21,839
Who says only men can inherit a title?

381
00:17:22,519 --> 00:17:23,200
Look at me.

382
00:17:23,279 --> 00:17:25,119
I am the leader of the Sacred Hand Sect.

383
00:17:25,119 --> 00:17:26,720
There is no reason you cannot claim

384
00:17:26,720 --> 00:17:27,800
the title of Bandit Prince.

385
00:17:28,960 --> 00:17:30,680
I never dared to think of it that way.

386
00:17:31,400 --> 00:17:33,119
But after hearing your advice,

387
00:17:33,400 --> 00:17:35,400
I should indeed talk to my father.

388
00:17:35,880 --> 00:17:36,759
Exactly.

389
00:17:36,759 --> 00:17:38,039
Women are just as capable as men.

390
00:17:39,480 --> 00:17:40,400
Take care, Sect Leader.

391
00:17:40,519 --> 00:17:41,079
I...

392
00:17:43,279 --> 00:17:44,599
I will take my leave now.

393
00:17:49,160 --> 00:17:49,799
I'm off.

394
00:17:57,812 --> 00:18:00,475
(Mao's Residence)

395
00:18:06,720 --> 00:18:07,400
Buyu!

396
00:18:36,325 --> 00:18:37,287
(Ministry of Justice)

397
00:18:37,319 --> 00:18:38,119
If you don't let go,

398
00:18:38,119 --> 00:18:39,260
I'm really going to be late.

399
00:18:39,680 --> 00:18:40,880
Are you still angry?

400
00:18:43,000 --> 00:18:44,160
If you have forgiven me,

401
00:18:44,160 --> 00:18:45,000
then I will let go.

402
00:18:45,559 --> 00:18:46,680
I'm not that petty.

403
00:18:47,090 --> 00:18:48,079
You should head back now.

404
00:18:48,200 --> 00:18:49,119
Once I'm off duty,

405
00:18:49,120 --> 00:18:50,360
I'll take you to see my family.

406
00:18:51,400 --> 00:18:52,240
What for?

407
00:18:52,680 --> 00:18:54,119
After everything that has happened,

408
00:18:54,279 --> 00:18:55,319
I think we should

409
00:18:55,319 --> 00:18:56,720
start preparing for our wedding.

410
00:18:57,279 --> 00:18:59,160
I want to bring you into the Mao family

411
00:18:59,400 --> 00:19:00,200
as soon as possible.

412
00:19:00,519 --> 00:19:01,319
Are you willing?

413
00:19:03,079 --> 00:19:03,839
I am.

414
00:19:04,987 --> 00:19:06,240
(Ministry of Justice)
Good. It is settled then.

415
00:19:06,400 --> 00:19:07,440
Go on home and wait for me.

416
00:19:07,925 --> 00:19:11,350
♪Casting aside all obsession
just to be with you♪

417
00:19:11,400 --> 00:19:12,160
(Ministry of Justice)
By the way, Chang,

418
00:19:14,359 --> 00:19:15,279
I don't want

419
00:19:15,279 --> 00:19:16,559
too many lies between us.

420
00:19:17,160 --> 00:19:18,240
Even the deepest bond

421
00:19:18,240 --> 00:19:20,170
can't withstand the test
of constant deception.

422
00:19:22,000 --> 00:19:22,799
Do you get it?

423
00:19:23,812 --> 00:19:27,712
♪Worlds apart, I wait our reunion♪
(Ministry of Justice)

424
00:19:27,800 --> 00:19:30,987
♪But I'll spend
my life keeping you safe♪

425
00:19:35,462 --> 00:19:38,737
♪Grudges and regrets
are like strong wine♪

426
00:19:38,775 --> 00:19:41,650
♪Drink it down and let it go♪

427
00:19:42,150 --> 00:19:47,868
♪An empty cup for our love and hate♪

428
00:19:49,050 --> 00:19:52,370
♪Tears blur a fate I can't control♪

429
00:19:52,500 --> 00:19:55,420
♪Let's drink until dawn♪

430
00:19:56,588 --> 00:20:01,828
♪Behind this mask, I'll never lie♪

431
00:20:03,050 --> 00:20:05,443
♪Every reunion feels like the first♪

432
00:20:05,443 --> 00:20:09,093
♪This hidden smile will never fade♪

433
00:20:09,162 --> 00:20:12,652
♪One heart, standing by your side♪

434
00:20:12,750 --> 00:20:15,725
♪To the ends of time♪

435
00:20:15,725 --> 00:20:19,100
♪The moon traces your face♪

436
00:20:19,287 --> 00:20:22,875
♪Draped in clouds, you fill my heart♪

437
00:20:22,875 --> 00:20:29,115
♪To find you
and keep our promise forever♪

438
00:20:29,450 --> 00:20:32,665
♪A silent prayer in my soul♪

439
00:20:32,950 --> 00:20:36,488
♪Carrying my vow beneath the moon♪

440
00:20:36,775 --> 00:20:39,800
♪Hoping we never drift apart again♪

441
00:20:39,800 --> 00:20:42,900
♪On our way to forever♪

442
00:20:42,900 --> 00:20:46,750
♪The moon traces your face♪

443
00:20:46,750 --> 00:20:50,110
♪Draped in clouds, you fill my heart♪

444
00:20:50,300 --> 00:20:56,260
♪To find you
and keep our promise forever♪

445
00:20:57,337 --> 00:21:06,977
♪Just to be with you♪
